for-all-mankind:

timemagazine:

This timelapse video shows the view from the Soyuz spacecraft as it is piloted by Russian Cosmonaut Gennady Padalka toward its docking with the International Space Station (@iss) on March 28, 2015. The video was released to TIME by @NASA on Thursday, May 21, 2015. TIME is following the yearlong mission by @StationCDRKelly and Russian Cosmonaut Mikhail Kornienko during their stay aboard the International Space Station. Follow the mission on time.com/space http://ift.tt/1SoqUwP

This video really shows the orbital maneuvering needed for station approach.
